#. type: SS
#, no-wrap
msgid "Keeping Time without External Synchronization"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid "This discussion is based on the following conditions:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Nothing is running that alters the date-time clocks, e.g., B<\\%ntpd>(1), "
"cron jobs, et al."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"The system timezone is configured for the correct local time.  See below "
"B<POSIX vs 'RIGHT'>."
